      "type": "text",
      "context": "div.w-layout-grid > div.contact19_item > p",
      "en": "We disclose greenhouse gas emissions and climate action plans annually through the Carbon Disclosure Project.",
      "cn": "我们每年通过碳披露项目公开温室气体排放与气候行动计划。"
    },
    {
      "id": "t63",
      "type": "text",
